{"type": "article", "id": 34284, "title": "这三个大“勺子”叠在一起，你猜它是个啥？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-09T23:09:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 19708, "name": "GT2P"}, {"id": 34769, "name": "KP Cykler"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 175, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161109192600ULaJKG5wBM3SEd8P.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Remolten by gt2P</h3><p>身处在拥有 200 多座火山的国家智利，来自 <a href=\"http://www.gt2p.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">gt2P</a> 工作室的设计师们对火山熔岩在家具领域的应用进行了一次相当大胆的尝试：火山岩先是被研磨成颗粒状，再经由两种不同的工艺塑造出了这套名为 Remolten 的凳子系列。比较粗糙的表面是在由不可溶的粉末模型上直接浇铸后冷却而成的，另一种覆盖在耐高温的材料表面的方法则获得了光滑的水滴状作品。对冷却的控制是加工过程中的关键一环，并且赋予了每一件作品独一无二的特性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165253rMX2jdoEYesyHDNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165253GJBOC9uibIYH7ow1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611091652534oUQ7Tv3YLnutWzG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698044\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165254xG4LZgQWIvqsKfk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.820293\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611091652548QxWdOJNbaFYHgjp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710269\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><p>          </p><h3>pokito by Andrew Brooks</h3><p>          </p><p>还记得我们上个月介绍的那款可以<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/33098.html\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">挤压的随行杯</a>吗？英国设计师 Andrew Brooks 带来的 pokito 也是一个扭一扭就能变形的随行杯，有着出色的便携性。杯子中间的分隔区间让它能够在不同的容量间转换，因为采用了细条纹增加摩擦，手握时也更加舒适。如果需要清洁，就算把它放进洗碗机中也不会受到影响。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1073445825/pokito\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 10 英镑。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109184514CtDeNdPKQaJLlswm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611091845156WzAyJMHYB4EPQiC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109184515BPtgIEX0saSGfTFh.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109184514sP7KSYVhTCvMWRIm.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611091845140HEp2TnNXkPgYyaB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109184514oI2gMt7mSz4sLFa3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Stealth by Stealth Fitness</h3><p>喜欢健身但觉得过程有些无聊，为什么我们不一边玩游戏一边健身呢？最近一个美国的<a href=\"http://www.gameyourcore.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计团队</a>就带来了一款将手机游戏与健身结合的设备 Stealth，当你用它做平板支撑的时候，把下载了配套游戏的手机放在上方的凹槽中，就可以把平板当作游戏操作杆一边闯关一边锻炼自己的肌肉了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/98545945/stealth-get-ripped-abs-by-playing-games-on-your-sm\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 129 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109185832EdKBwZVuGaNWsjD4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611091858321dMLkySARjICZheo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109185832kRS4LBeG6jFJaWqM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Infinium by Jayneel Shah</h3><p>印度产品设计学生 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/jayneel\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jayneel Shah</a> 最近带来了一件非常吸睛的黑胶唱片机 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/44885495/INFINIUM-A-Modern-Record-Player-Concept\" rel=\"nofollow\">Infinium</a>：分为三层的流线型设计让人一时间很难把它同唱片机联系在一起，尽管造型非常大胆，但它并没有跳脱出传统唱片机的结构。作为一款有着智能元素的机器，Shah 对操作方式进行了革新，将所有控制都整合在了最上方的触摸式界面上：滑动边缘即可调节音量、播放和暂停间的切换只要轻轻一拍、长按后还能切换至收音机模式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109191234ON3V2nYIWy9QFjDU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109191235fLwYvr7aIjBEhTkl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109191234pn7cMQCSYXiJKjz5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109191235Hj2OyxFsRVIimD5U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109191235jtBh8U5OuWRc6rGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Bike Hanger 2.0 by KP Cykler</h3><p>把自行车挂在墙上是不少人用来装饰房间并且提高空间利用率的方法，来自丹麦的自行车设计团队 <a href=\"https://kpcyclery.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KP Cykler</a> 在一年前曾经推出一款小巧耐用的自行车架，最近他们又推出了它的迭代款。被称为 2.0 的这一款自行车架采用了镀铬圆管，经过改良的把手则变得更加纤细。可以灵活调节的支架能够支持宽 60 厘米的自行车，保证它们悬挂时不会碰到墙壁。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/820118192/the-bike-hanger-20-beautiful-bicycle-storage\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 535 丹麦克朗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109173119Uk1RpvJ7GbT9HOfc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109173122BruMzdlyvn41LKG2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109173121raSNmXG2uE8WdbPO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109173119DjEHNJ9Z1Os6Llwo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109173132CKgsnhA9kymaH57R.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>OLKA by Andrew Walla</h3><p>如果你喜欢实用且简洁的手机配件，不妨来看看美国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/wallaandrew\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andrew Walla</a> 带来的这款概念品牌 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43676933/Olka\" rel=\"nofollow\">OLKA</a>。产品包括手机壳、圆形的移动电源和配套的充电线，类似大理石台面的风格与配件光滑的表面看起来相当和谐，明快但不张扬的配色给人一种相当舒适的视觉效果。Walla 设计的移动电源有着双头收线的功能，不使用的时候收在顶部的电源线就成了提手，还可以当作钥匙扣使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165231yQ9CSXBcpOGLfxjT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165230YzPAQrEoIbxnvqCh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.908571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165230DOadRqoFruLvhleM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.908571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161109165230wpPKYjOze08INiGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.908571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}